{"tid":2211070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共連他的14歲女兒都不放過　澳洲駐中記者說出恐怖經歷","createTime":"2020-09-21T01:46:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T01:52:24.000Z","uid":271829,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"03d89581fd0c78c207abc6362a129b8564eb0a05","tid":2211070,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T01:46:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/5TzpXGHe_Yu9J-jOXA5NURpcrCw=/862x575/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AZ6NZEA73VBYPMUU5TGTDYX26M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5TzpXGHe_Yu9J-jOXA5NURpcrCw%3D%2F862x575%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAZ6NZEA73VBYPMUU5TGTDYX26M.jpg&h=cadbaac8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n卡尼和妻兒在長城上的合影。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n中國日前逮捕中國環球電視網（CGTN）華裔澳洲籍主播成蕾，隨後又以涉嫌「國家安全案件」為由，強抓兩名澳洲駐中國記者問話，兩名記者最後決定逃離中國，使得中國自1970年代以來首次沒有澳洲認可媒體的駐中記者。事實上，中共早在2年前便開始威脅澳洲駐中記者，澳洲廣播公司（ABC）前駐北京辦公室主任卡尼（Matthew Carney）今日（9/21）撰文揭露他和家人兩年前在北京的恐怖經歷，並指出中共為逼迫他其自我內容審查，甚至把他的14歲女兒當作威脅手段。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n但一家人全在中國，卡尼不能冒著孩子被捕的風險。他和妻子帶著女兒前往公安部報到。負責此案的公安人員告訴他，他涉嫌違反簽證規定。卡尼追問，他的女兒為何也被要求到公安部報到，此時一名女性官員回說：「你的女兒已經14歲了，根據中國法律，她已經是成年人。中國是法治國家，所以她將被以違反簽證法起訴。」她接著反問卡尼：「你知道作為法治國家的我們有權拘留你的女兒嗎？」<br />\n這名女性官員繼續威脅卡尼：「卡尼先生，我們有權把你的女兒拘留在一個不公開的地點，而我必須告知你，那裡有其他成年人被關押。」此時護女心切的卡尼忍不住了，他回嗆表示，若女兒遭關押，他一定會讓此事升級成澳洲與中國政府之間的外交事件。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200921/6P73H77UIVERFLZSTWBBZIHA54/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200921%2F6P73H77UIVERFLZSTWBBZIHA54%2F&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZomVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=61f22a85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200921%2F6P73H77UIVERFLZSTWBBZIHA54%2F&h=2f74b243\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200921/6P73H77UIVERFLZSTWBBZIHA54/</a>"},{"pid":"822dfee51b681eb3d65c0979df4d3c6da70351ad","tid":2211070,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T01:47:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc33b11f46cb093dfedfde44a8844d2468fc71a9","tid":2211070,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T01:48:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d6dea5f52c4314f001a580d401fc8e4080a77ea","tid":2211070,"uid":51621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T01:49:09.000Z","msg":"國際線有任 請每日推Post<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZomVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=678af485\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a>"},{"pid":"45b7fd5beefff7ddb538100712504d5738631570","tid":2211070,"uid":301820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T01:50:03.000Z","msg":"支那魔鬼納粹國"},{"pid":"f55a854aab74999da2275052e6b7d21002f721dc","tid":2211070,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T01:50:04.000Z","msg":"中共殺人唔貶眼 自己國家D細路仔都走去生劏器官"},{"pid":"fbd6ef24818be9c814737f4805b0cd0494662d7b","tid":2211070,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T01:50:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c03e65205fd5a1e95f8d974f345e19873da0c70a","tid":2211070,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc33b11f46cb093dfedfde44a8844d2468fc71a9","tid":2211070,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T01:48:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T01:50:15